moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：27年傑迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e50672d6075d7b6b46f433239bd2a0b5635dac6","tid":105422,"uid":87363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實發生咩事沉左？<br />\n我指王<span style=\"color: red;\">傑</span><br />\n唔係個post</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英皇03年個時<br />\n<br />\n王傑聲稱被毒啞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我信架<br />\n因為佢把口真心得罪人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34eccbd5ee2b62c799124a5949984e100234b6f","tid":105422,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解個個都信佢訪問啲野係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢把聲搞到依加咁係自己攞嚟<br />\n<br />\n利申 好中意早期嘅佢 不過96年之後成個人變哂</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想佢唱多啲廣東歌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜.....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己攞嚟係？</blockquote><br />\n佢話自己吧聲係俾人落毒<br />\n但係根本就搵唔到把地突然差嘅轉捩點<br />\n佢係95年開始把聲已經差咗<br />\n入蛋記之後就愈來愈厚同沙 高音都已經上唔到<br />\n其實佢自己都應該知呢個問題<br />\n03年開始就成日上節目唱live之後都會搵藉口講點解把聲沙咗<br />\n雖然唔知佢係食煙成日飲咖啡用錯聲定係點<br />\n總知就一定唔係俾人落毒"},{"pid":"d4dd6d29a8158c975fdd86c5fe04c2e3c96f48e9","tid":105422,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T06:03:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a192d9df0ff13e446b9631cc97916ef5b6dddca7","tid":105422,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>王傑當年係台灣賣碟應該勁過所有香港偽人<br />\n<br />\nBetween, 佢應該大把水，點解宜家好似咁唔惦</blockquote><br />\n冇唔掂過<br />\n一直都好疊水<br />\n90年代已經過十億身家（90年代中全球賣碟過千萬隻）<br />\n<br />\n只係俾人搞<br />\n香港狗仔隊係咁屈佢精神病，好賭酗酒等等<br />\n佢唔滿意英皇成日搞9佢d音樂，鬧翻左，簽左英皇10年俾人雪左幾年<br />\n<br />\n睇佢d訪問就鄧佢嗰幾年慘<br />\n不過錢方面佢一直都大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係大陸唱幾隻歌已經六位數計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d805abb606945e87c92d63abdd88aeef99df9b1e","tid":105422,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T06:35:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解佢窮左，佢講過離婚果時比哂啲野前妻，加上又要&quot;膳&quot;養費，後來又比英皇雪，冇收入。<br />\n加拿大全盛時期有勁多跑車，間屋有高爾夫球場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入英皇簽十年我收左三千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce133620f79ab3b6e0410fe2988bbd47c2fd79f","tid":105422,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T06:35:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢最紅ge時候o係飛碟唱片（華納）<br />\n但係飛碟好chur要佢一年內出超多碟<br />\n佢最紅果陣瘦到皮包骨咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：27年傑迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩隻廣東兩隻國語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba650d281cc47b2c54711e8509dbf2f6e9ea1a9b","tid":105422,"uid":52132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"好紅"},{"pid":"0c8de900b2410c2c951ce9ed3a50f25457502e22","tid":105422,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqJT1UF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqJT1UF.jpg&h=c9927afc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/143720_6296f3abdefa3f775304046b5531b0e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F143720_6296f3abdefa3f775304046b5531b0e6.jpg&h=9047e708&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/143723_f576f8ef5dff21475682b232a6c0c93c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F143723_f576f8ef5dff21475682b232a6c0c93c.jpg&h=cbaa2b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n計埋心癮<br />\n王傑廣東歌仲有咩？"},{"pid":"b2d09beece71ff82000b6ca0718cd6e4c49b15de","tid":105422,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T06:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出道第一隻碟係差唔多冇宣傳情況下賣到三十萬隻（當時最勁果啲都係幾萬隻，1987年）<br />\n<br />\n人地搵佢拍電視劇，一個鐘片酬僅次鄭少秋。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鄭少秋當時係最高？</blockquote><br />\n譚詠麟賣左100萬隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有四天王當年打撚到王傑敗走香港<br />\n連登真係好多小學雞改歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a95346ba053baed94edc0cfdb8cfa4a9031cbb5","tid":105422,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T06:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqJT1UF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqJT1UF.jpg&h=c9927afc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/143720_6296f3abdefa3f775304046b5531b0e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F143720_6296f3abdefa3f775304046b5531b0e6.jpg&h=9047e708&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/143723_f576f8ef5dff21475682b232a6c0c93c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h